text:
Asahi, I want to wrap up the
written interview matter...

Eh? Again!?
I really want a break~

Oh, I see...
You must be tired...

We went to
several places today...

With school and everything,
we had to cram it all into today.

Looking forward to the live, but besides practice,
there's so much else to do~...

But it's all for the live...
You must be tired. Rest first, it's okay.

Yes! Then, Producer-san,
will you answer the interview?

Haha...
It can't be done like that.
